profile:
The Gutter Patrol is a locally operated business. We specialize in professional gutter cleaning, small eavestrough installs, downspouts, fascia and drip flashing. We are also experts in leak repair and use industry standard NPC Gutter seal. The Gutter Patrol provides quality service for your homes gutters in the Calgary area. We are City licensed, insured, and have eight years experience in eavestrough maintenance. For professional service call The Gutter Patrol today.

Our mission is to provide customers with quality service and excellent workmanship. The Gutter Patrol is dedicated to your homes eavestrough and we always do a thorough job. We want you to be happy with choosing The Gutter Patrol and work hard to ensure it is done correctly. We offer free estimates, and competative pricing.

profile:
At Mega Roofing & Exteriors Inc. we offer a wide range of high-quality exterior services throughout southern Alberta, specializing in all roofing applications, exterior cladding (including vinyl and cement board) soffit/fascia & eavestroughs both 5" & 6". We also offer 24 hour emergency repair response line for any of our services.
Our company's core values are Honesty & Integrity, and we take extreme pride in our workmanship & exceptional customer service. We strive to go above and beyond, to ensure every client's satisfaction, whether it is an eavestrough cleaning, small repair service or a complete exterior renovation (roof, siding, all soft metals). 
We have financing facilities available (OAC).

profile:
Welcome to Chinook Exteriors! We are Exterior Systems Specialists serving the Greater Calgary area.

We have the experience you can count on to produce the professional results that you expect.

At Chinook Exteriors, we supply, install, maintain and repair the exterior systems that prevent water from entering homes and buildings.

Our specialty is the installation of high quality soffits, fascias, eavestroughs and Gutter Clean System leaf guards to direct water away from roofs and foundations and provide proper air circulation throughout attic spaces

We are very proud of our excellent customer service, high quality products and the beautiful results achieved by our skilled craftsmen.

We  are also proud to offer the Gutter Clean System to our clients to keep their eavestroughs free of the leaves and debris that block the water flow and cause overflows, leaks and water damage.

Contact Chinook Exteriors now to book your FREE Estimate

Dorsch Roofing & Exteriors is a Calgary Roofing company that is family owned and operated. Tyson and Chris Dorsch bring to the table 14 years of experience in the Roofing industry. Dorsch Roofing & Exteriors offers quality service and honest workmanship that you know you can trust. Customer satisfaction comes first at Dorsch Roofing our work is not done until your satisfied. Whether you are looking for a re-roof, new home build, siding, Fascia or have any other questions regarding exterior work done on your home we are here to answer your questions. We pride ourselves on quality installations, backed by a 10-year warranty on our workmanship. We offer a huge selection of roofing and exterior materials from the best suppliers in the industry in order to ensure your project gets the best possible products as well as installation to match you budget.

We’ve been hanging eaves in Calgary for over 30 years. As experience goes, our contractors have it in spades.

When you choose us for your eavestrough or roof, you’re choosing a company that’s been through the booms and the busts. It takes a combination of good service, consistent workmanship, and industry expertise to stand the test of time.

Thirty years is a long time to work for, and earn, a reputation for great quality and no-nonsense business. Our customers know that they can rely on our workmanship, and that we will quote a competitive price to complete their project. This is what has kept us successful since 1984, and what we keep us successful 30 years from now.

Learn more about our eavestroughing services, siding services, or roofing services. We know that you have many choices, and we thank you for considering Big 5 Exteriors for your residential or commercial project!
